Ask HN: Could AI be used to create semi-coherent code for movies?
text: I wonder if movie studios could use AI to create more realistic code or commands for movies and hacking scenes. Someone who is not technologically literate could just describe what is happening in the scene and have the AI produce realistic code or terminal outputs for what they want.
